    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Strips of cloth passed from front to back between the legs, attached to and supported by a cord or band around the waist.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
